Introduction

Chaein is a South Korean singer, dancer and rapper signed with RBW. She is the Main Vocalist, Lead Dancer and Lead Rapper of the girl group PURPLE KISS. She participated in the first and third seasons of the reality TV show "K-Pop Star".

She debuted with PURPLE KISS on March 15, 2021, with the mini album “INTO VIOLET”, with the title track “Ponzona”.
